column1: # This file contains aggregated performance metrics averaged across iterations
# for each configuration (A1-A5) and target RPS level.
# - pods: Number of pods (always 1 for A-series)
# - target_rps: Requested RPS for the test
# - throughput_rps: Actual throughput achieved (average across iterations)
# - total_requests: Total requests processed (average across iterations)
# - *_ms: Same latency metrics converted to milliseconds
